Oscar-winning composer Marvin Hamlisch and journalist Terre Blair will marry on 
May 29, 1989, the couple has announced. Hamlisch, 44, has won three Oscars -- 
two for "The Way We Were" and one for "The Sting" -- a Tony award, four Grammys 
and a Pulitzer Prize for his music and writing. He will be musical director for 
next month's Academy Awards telecast. Blair, a former correspondent and 
producer for "The Today Show," "ABC Wide World of Sports," "P.M. Magazine" and 
