 -- Andrea Leeds, 
</P>
<P>
"Stage Door" 
</P>
<P>
"As an actor, no one could touch him. As a human being, no one wanted to touch 
him." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Walter Matthau, 
</P>
<P>
"The Sunshine Boys" 
</P>
