POSSESSIONS; WEST BANK (ISRAEL); GAZA STRIP; JERUSALEM; RACIAL RELATIONS -- 
ISRAEL; ARABS -- ISRAEL; JEWS -- ISRAEL; KOLLEK, TEDDY 
</P>
