APPOINTMENTS; TOWER, JOHN; SENATE (U.S.); VOTING; DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE (U.S.) 
-- CONTRACTS; CONSULTANTS; CONFLICT OF INTEREST; MORALITY; DRINKING; 
ALCOHOLISM; PRESSLER, LARRY 
</P>
